%F A069951 From _Nicolas Bělohoubek_, Apr 11 2026: (Start)
%F A069951 G.f.: (1 + x + 18*x^2 + 7*x^3 + x^4 - x^5 + 8*x^6 + 18*x^7 + 2*x^8 - x^9)/(1 - x^5)^2.
%F A069951 a(n) = 2*a(n-5) - a(n-10). (End)
